          "id": "AwsSolutions-SNS2",
          "reason": "CloudWatch alarms cannot publish to SNS topics encrypted with the AWS-managed key, and a dedicated CMK costs $1/mo for alert text that contains no financial data. Transport is TLS-enforced.",
        },
        {
          "id": "AwsSolutions-IAM4",
          "reason": "Lambdas use the AWS-managed AWSLambdaBasicExecutionRole policy for CloudWatch Logs only.",
        },
        {
          "id": "AwsSolutions-IAM5",
          "reason": "Wildcards are confined to the GoldFinch table index ARN form table/index/* (index access requires it).",
        },
        {
          "id": "AwsSolutions-L1",
          "reason": "Runtime is pinned to the Node LTS that the esbuild bundling target (node22) matches; upgrades happen deliberately in lockstep.",
        },
